<chapter id="chapter-configuration">
  <title>Configuration</title>

  <section id="dependencies">
    <title>Dependencies</title>

    <para>In order to use this project through Maven, including the following
    in your dependencyManagement section:</para>

    <programlisting>&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.geomajas.project&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;geomajas-project-sld-all&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;1.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>

    <para>You can now add the individual modules in your dependency section
    without version. Maven will also help to manage the version of the project
    dependencies.</para>
  </section>
</chapter>
